From Michael Covington Subject Re When are two people married in God's eyes In article A Michael C Davis writes it has to do with honoring the laws of the state and also to do with how people will perceive us it is culturally insensitive to declare yourself married without going through a civil I would go further if a couple are unwilling to have their commitment publicly witnessed and recorded that's prima facie evidence that the commitment isn't really Michael Covington Associate Research Scientist Artificial Intelligence Programs The University of Georgia phone Athens Georgia amateur radio